<p class="">These are the words then used: <blockquote><q>"In particular, I have emphasised that only in special cases, such as, for example, major changes of policy.…"</q></blockquote> Are there other special major cases?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
