                Dr. Morgan  (Warrington)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-e335febe-c81e-4e5e-ad59-4074d51d30fd" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
