                Mr. W. Griffiths  (Manchester, Exchange)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-a3b406fa-b7be-4a07-8344-6c48d9c3c5c8" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
