                Mr. Griffiths
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-a03f524e-6e60-41ce-87f8-356b9a3ec8bf" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
