                Mr. Nigel Birch  (Flint, West)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-1a1c5f8b-90b0-4f11-9272-dcf5272435f2" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
