    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Before the right hon. and learned Gentleman sits down could I ask him how he will vote?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-1a1c5f8b-90b0-4f11-9272-dcf5272435f2" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-03-14/debates/bd93d257-be42-4f0d-86bc-f5214473e055/SupplementaryEstimates#contribution-1a1c5f8b-90b0-4f11-9272-dcf5272435f2">
