        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-879cbcd6-d156-41ae-b1e6-ed1f3381d0e5'>
            
<p class="">attack upon the Government itself but as a concealed and cowardly attack upon the National Health Service devised by people who have not the honesty to make it openly.</p>
