w, E.)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Prior-Palmer, Brig. O</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Walker-Smith, D. C.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Lloyd, Selwyn (Wirral)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Profumo, J. D.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Ward, Hon. G. R. (Worcester)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Lockwood, Lt.-Col. J. C.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Raikes, H. V.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Ward, Miss I. (Tynemouth)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Longden, G. J. M. (Herts. S. W.)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Rayner, Brig. R.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Waterhouse, Capt C.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Low, A. R. W.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Redmayne, M.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Watkinson, H.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Lucas, Major Sir J. (Portsmouth, S.)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Remnant, Hon. P.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Watt, Sir G. S. Harvie</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Lucas, P. B. (Brentford)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Renton, D. L. M.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Webbe, Sir H. (London)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Lucas-Tooth, Sir H.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Roberts, H. (Handsworth)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Wheatley, Major M. J. (Poole)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Lyttelton, Rt. Hon. O.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Roberts, P. G. (Heeley)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>White, J. Baker (Canterbury)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p>